<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[زكي]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>: (ى ( {زَكِيَ) المالُ، <span class="c2">(كَرَضِيَ)</span> ،} يَزْكَى <span class="c3">{زَكاءً:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>أَهْملَهُ الجوهرِيُّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وقالَ ابنُ سِيدَه عَن اللَّحْيانيّ:</span> هِيَ لُغَةٌ فِي} زَكَا {يَزْكُو إِذا <span class="c2">(نَمَا وزادَ)</span> وأَثْمَرَ؛ <span class="c2">(} كَتَزكَّى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>(و) <span class="c3">{زَكِيَ}</span> يَزْكَى: إِذا <span class="c2">(عَطِشَ)</span> ؛ عَن ثَعْلَب؛<span class="c5"> وَأنْشد:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>كصاحِبِ الخَمْرِ {يَزْكَى كُلَّما بعدَتْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>عَنهُ وإنْ ذاقَ شِرْباً هَشَّ للعَلَلِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">ولكنَّ ابنَ سِيدَه أَوْرَدَه فِي الواوِ وقالَ:</span> إنَّما أَثْبَتّه فِي الواوِ ولِوُجُودِ زكو وعَدَم زكي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(} وزَكِيَّةٌ)</span> ،<span class="c5"> كغَنِيَّةٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(ة بينَ البَصْرَةِ وواسِطَ)</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وممَّا يُسْتدركُ عَلَيْهِ:</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَرضٌ <span class="c3">{زَكِيَّةٌ: طَيِّبَةٌ سَمِينَةٌ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>} وإزكى،<span class="c5"> بالكسْرِ:</span> قَرْيةٌ بعُمَان.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>ودَيْرُ {زَكَّى،<span class="c5"> بفتْحٍ فتَشْديدٍ مَقْصوراً:</span> أَحَدُ الدّيورِ ذَكَره أَبُو عُبيدٍ؛ وَقد ذُكِرَ فِي الكافِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
